17 fully-offline tests (no LLM, no DB, no network) covering:
- /v1/chat/completions OpenAI-compat contract, OWUI synthetic-task
  filtering, Continue echo, reset+QR-cookie clear, 400/503 paths
- InferenceRouter cascade: Groq-first, Groq->Cerebras fallback,
  full exhaustion order, INFERENCE_BACKEND=local disablement, and the
